column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  pz.z as photoz FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n JOIN PhotoObj AS p on p.objid = n.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = n.objid JOIN PhotoZ AS pz ON pz.objid = n.objid WHERE   s.class = GALAXY&&&
